<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA26">
<l>yāṉumeṉ ṉeñcu micaintoḻintōm valviṉaiyaik</l>
<l>kāṉu malaiyum pukakkaṭivāṉ ṟāṉō</l>
<l>riruḷaṉṉa māmēṉi yemmiṟaiyār tanta</l>
<l>varuḷeṉṉun taṇṭā laṭittu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I and my heart have ceased acquiring bad Karma,</l>
<l>in order to chase it away so that it enters forest and mountain,</l>
<l>twitching under the stick that is called grace given by our lord</l>
<l>with a body dark as darkness itself.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
